app_name: Groups Control Groups Photo and Video Editing Apps Video Merger and Splitter
app_description: Split and Merge your videos. This app allows you to merge your clips into one video. Also this app can split your video to multiple small clips with any duration. You can add background music crop trim add texts and video effects. Save your competed video videos or share with friends Easy fast and user friendly UI. The App is free and Premium features require a subscription or purchase.The subscription will automatically renew at the end of each term and your credit card will be charged through your iTunes account within 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can turn off auto renew at any time from your iTunes account settings but refunds will not be provided for any unused portion of the term. Turning off the auto renew subscription should be made at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.
